"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT disp.client_id\nFROM trans\nJOIN card ON trans.account_id = card.disp_id\nJOIN disp ON card.disp_id = disp.disp_id\nWHERE trans.operation = 'VYBER KARTOU'\n  AND trans.amount < (SELECT AVG(amount) FROM trans WHERE YEAR(date) = 1998)\n  AND YEAR(trans.date) = 1998;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the distinct client IDs of account holders who have made credit card transactions (withdrawals) in 1998 with amounts less than the average transaction amount for that year. The query uses the `operation` column to filter for credit card withdrawals and calculates the average transaction amount for 1998 to compare against."